 formación en línea completa de Usuario animada por nuestro formador-experto PrestaShop, sin salir de tu casa!</p>\r\n					<div class=\"gamification-tip-infobox-content-controls right\">\r\n						<a href=\"javascript:$.fancybox.close();\" class=\"button\">Cerca</a>\r\n						<a href=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=324&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.prestashop.com%2Fes%2Fformacion-prestashop%3Futm_source%3Dback-office%26utm_medium%3Dtraining%26utm_campaign%3Dback-office-ES%23training_11\"  class=\"button success\" target=\"_blank\">Saber màs</a>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<script>\r\n	$(document).ready( function () {\r\n		$(\'.gamification_fancybox\').bind(\'click\', function () {\r\n			id_advice = 324;			\r\n			popin_url = \'https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=\'+id_advice+\'&url=\';\r\n			$(\'.gamification-tip-infobox\').after(\'<img style=\"display:none\" src=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/api/getAdvicePopinImg/\'+id_advice+\'.png\" />\');\r\n		});\r\n	});\r\n</script>\r\n</div>'),
